latestIgtvVideos.title: Styling my Mom's Trousseau- Saree in different Styles
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
There is something really special about your Mom's Sarees ❤️ They never go out of STYLE !
Recently I digged into my Mom's wardrobe & I could find this gem in it ! She had this Saree for over 20 years & it still looks so elegant 😍

Girls ! I tell you, you never need to buy any new Saree if your mom has a good collection.

So here in my video I am draping this lovely saree from my Mom's Trousseau❤️ I hope you'll like my drapes & Style. 
Do lemme know in the comment section 👇🏻 (p.s : I don't knw if anyone noticed it but I scorched & burnt the saree mistakenly while ironing it 😛) -------------------

I wanted something private, meaningful, and close to my heart… and that’s exactly what it turned out to be 🎂💕Just the way I wanted 🤌🏻surrounded by family, loved ones, my two best friends, and a vibe full of love and warmth 🪬 ♥️ 
The décor by @craftedweddingsevents @shwetssarda 
was stunning — every detail was thoughtfully done..Thank you so much ❤️
and the cake? By @desserts_by_guilty_pleasure 
A dream! Beautifully designed and definitely the cherry on top. 

Big thanks to @rupzee___005 for managing everything so well 🫶🏻

And the main @richphotography.in 
Thank you for being my right hand 😅 cheers to our 5 years, we met exactly on my bday and back then it was my first bday shoot done by you ❤️ now we have many more to come 🙌🏻
